  "key_design_patterns": [
    "Template Method: OracleSnapshotChangeEventSource overrides hook methods of RelationalSnapshotChangeEventSource",
    "SPI Plugin: SnapshotLock / SnapshotQuery discovered via service loader, @ConnectorSpecific scoping",
    "LRU + last-lookup optimization in OracleDatabaseSchema for objectId->TableId resolution",
    "AS OF SCN flashback query in SelectAllSnapshotQuery and enhanceOverriddenSelect",
    "Savepoint-based lock: preSchemaSnapshotSavepoint rolled back in releaseSchemaSnapshotLocks",
    "Retry with Metronome: createDataEventsForTableCallable retries ORA-01466 up to maxRetries times with 5s sleep"
  ],

  "important_notes": [
    "PDB support: prepare() and close() call setSessionToPdb/resetSessionToCdb when pdbName configured",
    "Snapshot offset: delegates to connectorConfig.getAdapter().determineSnapshotOffset() (LogMiner/XStream/OLR adapters)",
    "LOB column handling: lobColumnsByTableId map used for unavailable value placeholder detection (CLOB/NCLOB/BLOB/SQLXML/extended VARCHAR>4000/NVARCHAR>2000)",
    "NO_SUCH_TABLE sentinel in objectIdToTableId prevents repeated linear scans for unknown object IDs",
    "ORA-01466: table metadata changed during flashback query — triggers snapshot retry"
  ],

